snippet.title: Brigand Trailer
snippet.description:
A trailer for Brigand: Oaxaca, a challenging FPS/RPG hybrid by Laughing Coyote Software set in post-apocalyptic Mexico.

Steam Store Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/652410/Brigand_Oaxaca/
